    "body": "2020/03/08 -   Last weekend I celebrated my 1st vegan-bday! ğŸ¥³ This adventure has just began and Iâ€™ve already had great surprises, met amazing people, and saw I can change the world! It all started with my quest to improve my nutrition, because I love to take good care #tgc of my body and health ğŸ§–â€â™‚ï¸. Most people donâ€™t realize, but our food is fundamental for an optimum health (together with rest ğŸ§˜â€â™‚ï¸ and exercise ğŸ’ª). But soon, reading trustworthy sources (attention to fake news) I saw veganism has far more benefits than simply health:  itâ€™s also about #tgc and respecting animals (not just pets, everyone), and also about #tgc and preserving our planet (the only one we got ğŸ˜‰)All people I met after I started this adventure are good, some even curious:  where do you get your proteins? why such an â€œextremeâ€ choice? but and milk/eggs/honey? ğŸ®ğŸ”ğŸSome are already vegan (they inspire me, and often share â€œvegan secretsâ€ about conquering the world ğŸ¤« cooking). And some even said I inspired them to make conscious choices (I love to hear I inspired someone to #tgc of their self)!  Â« Run to the rescue with love and peace will follow Â»  â€” Joaquin Phoenix (Oscars 2020) And nowâ€¦ The famous recipes! ğŸ˜‹ CHOCOLATE CAKE:  325g flour 100g cocoa 20g baking powder 200g sugar Â½ tsp. of salt 500ml vegetable milk 1 tsp. of vanilla extract 60ml vegetable oil of neutral tasteMix all dry ingredients; Mix the dry and wet ingredients in an electric mixer; Cook for 45min in a 175Â°C temperature. Tooping ingredients:  150g of dark chocolate 100ml of vegetable milk 75g of icing sugar Â½ tsp. of vanilla extractMelt the chocolate in a double boiler; Mix all the other ingredients; Wait a few minutes and then cover the whole cake; Eat the delicious cake! CHOCOLATE MOUSSE:  175g of dark chocolate 150g of aquafabaMelt the chocolate in a double boiler; Beat the aquafaba with an electric mixer until it becomes whisked aquafaba (â€œsnow whiteâ€ texture); Mix them both well; Put in the refrigerator for at least a few hours (between 4h and 48h, your pick); Eat the delicious mousse! And you: how do you improve your life? "
